I found this dresser in the trash…
Credit: @maggiemcgaugh 
And I almost put it right back where I found it. 😂 This was an annoying flip! Between SUPER thick paint and primer, hand making a stencil, running out of sandpaper, and having major anxiety about trying a new style... it was all worth it!
All tools are linked in my bio.

Heat gun: @wagnerspraytech
Sander: @blackanddecker_us
